{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">An captivating game in the soulslike genre with an original system of magic spells, which is based on a combination of runic symbols.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will have to fight as the princess of the mysterious island Buyan, located between the worlds \u2014 the world of the living and the kingdom of the dead.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348640/extras/Tsarevna_Steam_Gif_Ballerina_v002.gif?t=1733158231\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">An ancient evil has invaded the island to find a powerful artifact capable of destroying the whole world. Your task is to prevent this.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Enjoy a thoughtful combat system</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get ready for dynamic battles in the spirit of soulslike games, where cold steel and magic complement each other, and the visual effects of using magic will give aesthetic pleasure even to the most sophisticated player.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348640/extras/Tsarevna_Steam_Gif_Attack_v002.gif?t=1733158231\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Fight against unique opponents</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You'll be amazed by the diversity and uniqueness of the enemies and bosses.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each battle with a new boss will require the player to react and to choose the optimal attack tactics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348640/extras/Tsarevna_Steam_Gif_Boss_v002.gif?t=1733158231\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Upgrade your abilities</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">An extensive system of magical abilities, character customization and cold steel will give you rich experience.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348640/extras/Tsarevna_Steam_Gif_Clothes_v002.gif?t=1733158231\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Explore the island\u00a0</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Colorful locations full of riddles, chests filled with craft items and other artifacts are waiting for you.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will definitely want to return to the world of the game to enjoy the beauty of the mysterious island again.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348640/extras/Tsarevna_Steam_Gif_Run_v002.gif?t=1733158231\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348640/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733158231","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348640/page.bg.jpg?t=1733158231","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348640/9cdec25fa6677df6a3cd9921dfcc8f0c4afe0b1a/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733158231","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3348640/9cdec25fa6677df6a3cd9921dfcc8f0c4afe0b1a/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733158231","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen PvP","id":37},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen Co-op","id":39},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Captions available","id":13},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Stats","id":15},{"description":"Remote Play Together","id":44}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],